a Culatra","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5031_ilha_da_culatra_1016_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5031_ilha_da_culatra_1016_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":36.98891,"longitude":-7.833611},"summary":"Grab your beach parasol and head to Ilha da Culatra for the day. ","url":"/poi/algarve/ilha-da-culatra","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0243","title":"Loulé Carnival","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0243_loule_carnival_517302360_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0243_loule_carnival_517302360_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1389,"longitude":-8.022492},"summary":"If you want to explore a lesser-known side of the Algarve, Loul&eacute; is a great place to start. ","url":"/poi/algarve/loule-carnival","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0144","title":"Mercado de Loulé","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_market_of_loule_926778726_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_market_of_loule_926778726_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1385422,"longitude":-8.02216148},"summary":"Discover Mercado de Loul&eacute;, an incredible covered market in this traditional town's heart. ","url":"/poi/algarve/mercado-de-loule","category":"Shopping Beaches"},{"code":"","title":"Mercado Municipal Market","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/faro city/bjv_altinkum_markets_gens_0713_01_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/faro city/bjv_altinkum_markets_gens_0713_01_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.02024,"longitude":-7.928533},"summary":"An impressive building in the heart of town, the Mercado Municipal de Faro is a lovely, cool place to come for a wander and to pick up fresh, local produce and people-watch. ","url":"/poi/algarve/mercado-municipal-market","category":"Shopping Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0066","title":"Monchique Mountains","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0066_monchique_mountains_544801578_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0066_monchique_mountains_544801578_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.3111,"longitude":-8.594789},"summary":"Potter along the narrow cobbled streets enjoying a honey-soaked cake from one of the many cake shops or take in the restorative spa waters at Caldas de Monchique. ","url":"/poi/algarve/monchique-mountains","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia de Vale do Lobo","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_vale_de_lobo_golf_courses_636247404_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_vale_de_lobo_golf_courses_636247404_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.04789,"longitude":-8.064724},"summary":"Backed by red-tinged cliffs and carpeted in golden sand, Praia de Vale do Lobo is a real stunner. ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-de-vale-do-lobo","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia do Ancao","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_generic_beach_1213510191_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_generic_beach_1213510191_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.03276,"longitude":-8.038634},"summary":"Part of Ria Formosa Natural Park, Praia do Ancao is a long sandy beach backed by sand dunes and pine trees. ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-do-ancao","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia do Garrao","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_praia_de_garrao_nascente_980105990_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_praia_de_garrao_nascente_980105990_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.039608,"longit