_860247974_0918.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1527519,"longitude":-7.889201},"summary":"Swing by the old-school village of S&atilde;o Br&aacute;s to discover the Algarve at its most authentic. ","url":"/poi/algarve/sao-bras","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0245","title":"Seven Hanging Valleys Walking trail ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0245_sete_vales_in_lagoa_699910450_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0245_sete_vales_in_lagoa_699910450_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.08791,"longitude":-8.415715},"summary":"<p>Pinch-me panoramas are on the cards along this coastal cliff walk with its surf-splashed rock formations and secret coves. ","url":"/poi/algarve/seven-hanging-valleys-walking-trail","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0068","title":"Silves","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0068_silves_479077489_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0068_silves_479077489_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.18874,"longitude":-8.440215},"summary":"If you love old-world charm, you’ll love the former capital of the Algarve where you can lunch in cafés along the River Arade or take in the expansive views of the countryside from the red-bricked castle. ","url":"/poi/algarve/silves","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0059","title":"Slide & Splash Waterpark","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0059_slide_and_splash_waterpark_0414_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0059_slide_and_splash_waterpark_0414_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.13931,"longitude":-8.473315},"summary":"Water slides, spa treatments &ndash; yep, you'll find them all at Slide &amp; Splash! ","url":"/poi/algarve/slide-splash-waterpark","category":"Acti